bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084506/brakeace-app-interface-shows-braking-data-flow-score-748x420.jpg 748w\"></a></p><p>The BrakeAce App collates data from your braking, analyses it with a fancy algorithm, then shows you three specific locations on the trail where your braking could’ve been more efficient to allow you to carry more speed through that section.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084530/brakeace-turn-analysis.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084530/brakeace-turn-analysis.jpg\" alt=\"brakeace turn analysis opportunities to carry more speed\" width=\"1200\" height=\"676\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084530/brakeace-turn-analysis.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084530/brakeace-turn-analysis-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084530/brakeace-turn-analysis-800x451.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084530/brakeace-turn-analysis-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084530/brakeace-turn-analysis-768x433.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084530/brakeace-turn-analysis-696x392.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084530/brakeace-turn-analysis-1068x602.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084530/brakeace-turn-analysis-746x420.jpg 746w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb20 src ng ngcb20 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084530/brakeace-turn-analysis.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084530/brakeace-turn-analysis.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084530/brakeace-turn-analysis-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084530/brakeace-turn-analysis-800x451.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084530/brakeace-turn-analysis-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084530/brakeace-turn-analysis-768x433.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084530/brakeace-turn-analysis-696x392.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084530/brakeace-turn-analysis-1068x602.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084530/brakeace-turn-analysis-746x420.jpg 746w\"></a></p><p>It effectively looks to replace a mountain bike coach who will be able to give you that same information by watching you ride. That said, there is potential for coaches to use this too, to help them help their customers to ride better.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084519/brakeace-flow-score-pro-versus-beginner.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/01084519/brakeace-flow-score-pro-versus-beginner.jpg\" alt=\"brakeace flow score beginner versus pro\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" data-ezsrcset=\"http