y is February 2022.</p><p>Can’t wait that long? BrakeAce will send you a prototype set (the same sensors currently being used by big brands), if you pledge $5,083 (NZ), by August 2021.</p><p><span><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0QnoR6kLypU?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\"></iframe></span></p><p><a href=\"https://www.brakeace.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>BrakeAce.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"2530733af2c58edda639a23aac683ea3ff3c143ade9a1e383b950b4395111e17","category":"Cycling"}